# 🤖 Cursor Usage Rules

- “Create a new page” → generate under `pages/`.
- “Create a new test” → generate under `tests/`.
- “Update a test/page” → modify the existing file.
- When unsure, ask clarifying questions before generating code.
- When creating from scratch, update an existing file instead of creating a new one.
- All flaky tests **must** be tagged `@flaky`.
